reviews.text:
Convenient restaurant to try Cantonese foods. Waitresses are very nice. Good food.
a lot of choices... try the fish!
Good service, environment is bright, space not too cramp, food is generally good, except the beef balls, taste funny
The portion very small n a bit expensive but the taste quite good

This typical chinese restaurant serves delicious local dishes despite the fact that it does costs a little more extras but still it is worth coming to eat. 
Nice ambient with friendly staffs all ready to assist. 
They have limited choices for desserts. 
The one we went to is at Visionary in Tung Chung. Suggest not to go when the weather is wet or cloudy unless U drives as there is no shelter walking to and from the main road. 
I will give the maximum thumbs up on their delicious food 👍👍👍👍👍.
loved, noodle soup is best

reviews.text: 개인적으로 홍콩에서 먹어본 음식 중 가장 맛있는 음식에 들어갈 정도로 괜찮아요. 가격도 괜찮은 편이고, 맛도 아주 좋아요. 누구든지 무난하게 드실 수 있는 음식들입니다. 강추 합니다. 저는 자주 방문할 것 같아요.
咸水角，梅菜燒賣好好食！孖寶抵食！食物水準不錯！差左地點較遠！
食物方面，要改進眉立磁巴，皮太差，點心份量不太好。

Convenient restaurant to try Cantonese foods. Waitresses are very nice. Good food.
a lot of choices... try the fish!
Good food and warm service! We tried 客家炒飯、冬瓜盅、家常豆腐、大澳骨 which are all good. 霸王雞 was fine but slightly overcooked. Staff was helpful.
